Subject: [PATCH] hw: add VAMS management peripherals

Add the firmware-facing mailbox, watchdog, reset, and telemetry device to the
VAMS RV32 machine.  Management resets restore ELF-backed SRAM contents while
retaining reset-cause telemetry, allowing deterministic watchdog recovery.

---

